<sect1 id="bigreqsproto" xreflabel="bigreqsproto-&bigreqsproto-version;">
  <?dbhtml filename="bigreqsproto.html"?>

  <title>bigreqsproto-&bigreqsproto-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      This extension defines a protocol to enable the use of requests that
      exceed 262140 bytes in length.
    </para>

